            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>tortiglioni</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> with a large pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the<strong> tortiglioni</strong> for 7-8 min or until cooked with a slight bite, then drain and return to the pot</p><p>Tip: It doesn't need to be fully cooked, as it will finish cooking in the sauce later!</p><p>Wash your <strong>spinach</strong>, then pat dry with kitchen paper</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
