      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the courgette has started to brown, add the <strong>creamy stock</strong>, <strong>spinach </strong>and <strong>Tenderstem broccoli </strong>to the pan<strong> </strong>and cook, covered, for 3-4 min further or until the spinach has wilted and the sauce has begun to thicken</p>",
      "order": 6,
